divs: Sighting DetailsI walked outside and looked up at Jupiter and just below and a little to the north were what looked like two stars. They were very bright and did not seem to be moving. While I was looking at them they slowly faded away and did not come back. I would like to Know if anyone else saw this. They didn't seem to move at all just faded away.
